item.title: Weekly Review #53 - Three Blank Months, Life Adrift, and Spring Festival
item.description: 'Special Person - Khalil Fong' Preface This piece is a record and reflection of my life from December 4, 2023, to February 29, 2024. Much has transpired over the past few months, across various dimensions of life, making it challenging to begin writing this weekly review, which was originally intended to document daily life and personal thoughts.
